Package: whois-nameservers
Version: 2.23626
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: NikkyBun <89685096+NikkyBun@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: libc6
Installed-Size: 12200
Description: WHOIS Nameserver Batch Lookup
 Desktop GUI tool to look up domain nameservers for many domains at once
 via WHOIS and DNS. Self-contained build that bundles Python and Tk, so no
 extra runtime packages are required.
